  "Description": {
    "English": "Installed into the drive system aboard the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Nautilon Submarine</span>.<br><br>Captures energy by exploiting the saline gradient in deep water environments, allowing a slow recharge of the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Humboldt Drive</span> in the event of fuel emergencies.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "安装在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">大鹦鹉螺潜水艇</span>搭载的驱动系统当中。<br><br>能在燃料稀缺时，利用深水环境中的盐水梯度获取能量，为<span class=\"name name-technology\">洪堡驱动器</span>缓慢充能。",
    "TencentChinese": "安装在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">大鹦鹉螺潜水艇</span>搭载的驱动系统当中。<br><br>能在燃料稀缺时，利用深水环境中的盐水梯度获取能量，为<span class=\"name name-technology\">洪堡驱动器</span>缓慢充能。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "安裝於<span class=\"name name-stellar\">巡洋龍潛艇</span>的驅動器系統中。<br><br>利用深海環境的鹽份差異擷取能量，在燃料緊急情況下可以緩慢為<span class=\"name name-technology\">洪保德驅動器</span>充電。"
  },
